txt_content:
Hello大家好我是Java！
今天给大家带来的是一个本人创作的1.9小模组，看到标题就知道熊孩子必备有木有～
这就是爆炸弓啦！
在这里，我做了一个一键生成版，可以让大家更方便地体验到！



指令：
/summon FallingSand ~ ~1 ~ {Block:redstone_block,Time:1,Passengers:[{id:FallingSand,Block:activator_rail,Time:1,Passengers:[{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/fill ~1 ~ ~2 ~-1 ~ ~10 glass_pane},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/setblock ~ ~ ~3 redstone_block},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/setblock ~ ~ ~4 repeating_command_block 3 1 {Command:/testfor @e[type=Arrow] {inGround:1b}}}
,{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/setblock ~ ~ ~5 chain_command_block 11 1 {Command:/execute @e[type=Arrow] ~ ~ ~ /summon LightningBolt ~ ~ ~}}
,{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/setblock ~ ~ ~6 chain_command_block 11 1 {Command:/execute @e[type=Arrow] ~ ~ ~ /summon LightningBolt ~ ~ ~}},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/setblock ~ ~ ~7 chain_command_block 11 1 {Command:/execute @e[type=Arrow] ~ ~ ~ /summon LightningBolt ~ ~ ~}},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/setblock ~ ~ ~8 chain_command_block 11 1 {Command:/execute @e[type=Arrow] ~ ~ ~ /summon Creeper ~ ~ ~ {powered:1,ExplosionRadius:5,ignited:1,Fuse:0}}},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/setblock ~ ~ ~9 chain_command_block 11 1 {Command:kill @e[type=Arrow]}},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/fill ~1 ~-1 ~2 ~-1 ~-1 ~10 quartz_block},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/fill ~1 ~1 ~2 ~-1 ~1 ~10 quartz_block},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/fill ~ ~1 ~3 ~ ~1 ~9 redstone_block},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/fill ~1 ~2 ~2 ~-1 ~2 ~10 obsidian},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/fill ~1 ~-2 ~2 ~-1 ~-2 ~10 obsidian},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/say ——————————},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/say 模组－爆炸弓},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/say Java制作},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/say 未经允许不得转载},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/say ——————————},{id:MinecartCommandBlock,Command:/setblock ~ ~-1 ~ quartz_block}]}]}

